car.shared.input
Interface SliderImpl

All Known Implementing Classes:
SliderImplGeneral, SliderImplMozilla
public interface SliderImpl

The interface specifying functions required for an implementation for the Slider class. GWT's deferred binding is used to create an instance of the appropriate implementing class.

Author:
Joshua Little
